<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="9Jul1933"><font color="red">9 July 1933</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): However, I go on with the damn thing. Yesterday I walked 8 km by myself. I have also worked, as well as I could, about 3&frac12; hours per day. </div>
